{"tid":798154,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實搭巴士返青衣真係好撚慘","createTime":"2018-08-29T05:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T15:06:08.000Z","uid":72327,"like":7,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"be73ab7a2f1b2f38fb694d478fc52447bd025871","tid":798154,"uid":72327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:40:50.000Z","msg":"如果搭巴士見到靚女, 果一日嘅心情就會靚哂<br />\n可惜偏偏青衣呢個地方, 係無靚女會搭巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能靚女唔會去荃灣, 所以由荃灣返去青衣都唔會見到有靚女<br />\n但係連星期六日夜晚係尖沙咀, 旺角搭41A返青衣都可以全車係阿叔阿嬸<br />\n就連平日收工時間諗住灣仔銅鑼灣會多少少OL, 點撚知都係全部阿叔阿嬸!!<br />\n究竟係我唔好彩? 定青衣真係成為左老人區?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我想問, 搭成個鐘巴士同個臭汗肥仔一齊坐, 可以點忍到落車?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433550393fb54b4f1f441dd1f405d166e971207e","tid":798154,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:42:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca3ff5048e4ee382cb59617f13cbc397f6230364","tid":798154,"uid":72327,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"433550393fb54b4f1f441dd1f405d166e971207e","tid":798154,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:42:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:45:00.000Z","msg":"對唔住囉<br />\n單手打緊字 將就下啦"},{"pid":"4de5f40737040f0efe822c29ea6ce3bfe7131d6b","tid":798154,"uid":121060,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:47:17.000Z","msg":"試下搭巴士去天水圍，天水圍都幾多靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f036ece00ef033fad6b0437c21b6a012255f8e2","tid":798154,"uid":72327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4de5f40737040f0efe822c29ea6ce3bfe7131d6b","tid":798154,"uid":121060,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:47:17.000Z","msg":"試下搭巴士去天水圍，天水圍都幾多靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:48:06.000Z","msg":"有冇話邊一架多?"},{"pid":